echomind (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major release with comprehensive enhancements
  * Added multiple API provider support (chat, chatanywhere, openai, claude, ollama)
  * Added interactive REPL mode for multi-turn conversations
  * Added streaming responses with real-time display
  * Added configuration system with TOML support
  * Added progress indicators and colored output
  * Modular architecture with custom error types
  * Comprehensive test suite
  * CI/CD pipeline with GitHub Actions
  * Enhanced documentation

